description:
The evil Homeowners’ Association has plucked Dadish from the radish patch, and it’s up to his eldest son, DJ, to rescue him.

Explore 50 tricky levels, battle food-themed foes, and try not to get squished by a tunnel-boring machine. Can DJ save his dad before it's too late? There’s no time to lose in this classic platforming adventure!

• An action packed platforming adventure
• Fun for new players and long time Dadish fans
• Swing from vines, ride conveyors and bounce off clouds
• 50 hand crafted stages
• Sassy baby radishes, possums and more
• Get a lift with a giant flying hamburger
• Ride on your mom's back, she is a tomato
• Defeat the five evil staff members of the Homeowners' Association
• Cool soundtrack, I even rap on this one a little bit
• Dialogue that is sort of funny
• Make your dad proud
